<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 09:13:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>香港企业关门歇业，城市在大流行后艰难复苏</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-businesses-shut-shop-city-struggles-revive-post-pandemic-2024-04-30/</link><description>十多年前，当 48 岁的 Jacky Yu 在香港开设日本礼品店时，旺角的旅游和购物区是一个熙熙攘攘的中心，挤满了摊位、街头小吃和游客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-businesses-shut-shop-city-struggles-revive-post-pandemic-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商金科已准备好法院主导的重组初步计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-jinke-has-prepared-initial-plan-court-led-restructure-2024-04-30/</link><description>开发商金科地产集团上周成为首家被国内法院接受重组的中国上市开发商，周二告诉投资者，该公司已制定了一份初步的债务重组计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:13:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-jinke-has-prepared-initial-plan-court-led-restructure-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示哈马斯和法塔赫表达了和解的政治意愿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-hamas-fatah-express-political-will-reconciliation-2024-04-30/</link><description>中国外交部周二表示，巴勒斯坦敌对组织哈马斯和法塔赫在北京举行的团结会谈上表达了通过对话寻求和解的政治意愿。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 08:09:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-hamas-fatah-express-political-will-reconciliation-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>面对国内外挑战，中国将召开重要的党的“全会”以进一步实现国家现代化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-will-hold-key-third-plenum-july-2024-04-30/</link><description>中国共产党中央委员会将于 7 月召开一次重要会议，即全会，这是自 2022 年选出精英决策者机构以来的第三次会议，重点讨论国内“挑战”和广泛复杂性中的改革。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:17:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-will-hold-key-third-plenum-july-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>嘉士伯表示，尽管中国啤酒市场表现平淡，但第一季度的增长仍由高端品牌推动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-q1-sales-slightly-above-forecast-guidance-unchanged-2024-04-30/</link><description>丹麦啤酒制造商嘉士伯首席执行官周二表示，第一季度其优质啤酒品牌销量有所增加，所有主要市场的价格均有所上涨，但中国的啤酒饮用者仍持观望态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 06:05:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-q1-sales-slightly-above-forecast-guidance-unchanged-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉进军中国自动驾驶市场面临竞争对手的追赶</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-self-driving-bid-china-faces-rivals-racing-ahead-2024-04-30/</link><description>如果特斯拉成功将其“全自动驾驶”系统引入全球最大的汽车市场中国，这家美国电动汽车先驱将驶入全球自动驾驶汽车竞赛的快车道。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:06:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-self-driving-bid-china-faces-rivals-racing-ahead-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>快时尚巨头 Shein 也想销售护肤品、牙膏和玩具</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fast-fashion-giant-shein-wants-sell-skincare-toothpaste-toys-too-2024-04-30/</link><description>在线快时尚零售商 Shein 正在吸引牙膏集团高露洁棕榄 (Colgate-Palmolive) 和玩具制造商孩之宝 (Hasbro) 等品牌，试图在其平台上销售更多家喻户晓的品牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:04:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/fast-fashion-giant-shein-wants-sell-skincare-toothpaste-toys-too-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>所罗门群岛投票选出下一任领导人，亲中国的索加瓦雷退出竞选</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pro-china-sogavare-out-race-solomon-islands-votes-next-leader-2024-04-30/</link><description>所罗门群岛总理马纳西·索加瓦雷(Manasseh Sogavare)拉近了该国与中国的距离，使美国更加关注太平洋岛屿的战略重要性，但在选举结果未果后，他退出了领导人竞选。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:25:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pro-china-sogavare-out-race-solomon-islands-votes-next-leader-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商花样年提出新重组条款，股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-fantasia-proposes-new-restructuring-terms-shares-up-2024-04-30/</link><description>陷入困境的中国房地产开发商花样年周一表示，已与其债券持有人特设小组达成新协议，以新票据和股票重组其 40 亿美元债券。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 03:18:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-developer-fantasia-proposes-new-restructuring-terms-shares-up-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾指责中国在有争议的南海浅滩损坏其船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-expels-philippine-vessels-scarborough-shoal-state-media-says-2024-04-30/</link><description>菲律宾周二指责中国海警在南海争议海域骚扰并损坏其一艘船只，并否认北京方面已将两艘船只驱逐出争议激烈的浅滩的立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:35:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-expels-philippine-vessels-scarborough-shoal-state-media-says-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织表示，亚洲央行有能力独立于美联储采取行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia-pacific-economies-headed-soft-landing-says-imf-2024-04-30/</link><description>国际货币基金组织周二表示，亚洲相对较低的通胀意味着该地区央行在制定货币政策时可以更多地关注国内状况，而不是美联储可能采取的行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:23:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia-pacific-economies-headed-soft-landing-says-imf-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>万科首单商业REIT上市首日收盘持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vankes-first-public-commercial-reit-falls-early-trade-debut-2024-04-30/</link><description>万科首个公开商业地产投资产品周二首日收盘持平，反映出在房地产市场长期低迷的情况下，人们对这家中国第二大开发商的谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:09:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-vankes-first-public-commercial-reit-falls-early-trade-debut-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>股价在充满动静的一周中面临月度下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二，在一系列经济数据、财报和美联储政策会议公布之前，全球股市出现六个月来首次月度下跌，而日元在疑似干预措施从 34 年低点提振一天后走软。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:04:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国工厂活动创14个月来最快增速</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-fastest-clip-14-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的一项私人调查显示，在新出口订单强劲增长的推动下，4月份中国制造业活动以14个月以来最快的速度扩张，这对于仍在努力实现强劲复苏的经济来说是一个令人鼓舞的迹象。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 02:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-factory-activity-expands-fastest-clip-14-months-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-04-30/</guid></item><item><title>4月份中国工厂、服务业活动增速放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</link><description>周二的官方调查显示，中国四月份制造业和服务业增长放缓，表明世界第二大经济体在第二季度初失去了动力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:59:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-grows-slower-pace-april-2024-04-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>